title: L'Oreal Dermo-Expertise Sublime Bronze Self-Tanning Gelee, Medium-Natural , 5 fl oz (150 ml)
description: Sublime Bronze Gelee's unique ultra-lightweight formula applies easily and dries quickly. Made with Vitamin E and gentle Alpha Hydroxyl Acid (AHA) derivative, Sublime Bronze Self-Tanning Gelee for Medium Natural Tan leaves your skin feeling soft and smooth.  Gelee for Medum Natural Tan will be two shades darker than your natural skin tone. Results may vary. Continue to use Sublime Bronze until you have reached your desired level of tan.
